query:
SELECT 
  lps.pageId,
  lps.colorScheme,
  cs.id as color_scheme_id,
  cs.name as color_scheme_name,
  cs.primaryColor,
  cs.secondaryColor
FROM landing_page_settings lps
LEFT JOIN color_schemes cs ON lps.colorScheme = cs.slug
WHERE lps.pageId = 'black-friday';
